    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given the narrow COU scope limited to ASTM F1717 static compression-bending of the non-cannulated design; no extrapolation to other loading modes is claimed. Comprehensive Monte Carlo UQ (n=2000) confirms all three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and <10% relative error against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. The FEA modeling framework is accepted as credible for the stated COU.",
